<h2 class="bac">Our Business:</h2>
<p class="bac">
In some countries, securities, strategic advisory and other investment banking activities are performed by investment banking affiliates of Bank of America. In South Africa, this is Merrill Lynch. 
</p>
<p class="bac">
Merrill Lynch has been operating in South Africa since 1997, following the acquisition of stockbroker Smith Borkum Hare. The company&#39;s offices are located in Sandton, Johannesburg. The local team offers a strong equities business with highly&ndash;rated sales, sales trading and research capabilities to meet the needs of a domestic and international client base.  
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Overview:</h2>  
<p class="bac">
As an Analyst, you&#39;ll: 
</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Take a 12&ndash;month rotational programme</li>
	<li>Experience rotations through Global Markets, Investment Banking and Research </li>
	<li>Gain in&ndash;depth introduction to the company, its culture and global reach, alongside other newly&ndash;hired analysts</li>
	<li>Begin your career with a training programme to help you develop the business, financial and analytical skills needed to hit the ground running when you join your group </li>
	<li>Work with, and learn from, teams of professionals across the company, including senior experts within your group, and other areas of the company, as well as colleagues from around the globe</li>
	<li>Build relationships, knowledge and experience that will open doors to a wide range of future career options and opportunities</li>
	<li>Discover unlimited opportunities to challenge yourself and grow professionally</li>
	<li>Collaborate on exciting projects that contribute to business success and next&ndash;generation advances</li>
</ul>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Qualifications:</h2>
<p class="bac">
Strong academic qualifications and quantitative skills are important. Equally important are initiative, strategic and creative thinking, communication skills and a genuine interest in financial markets. 
</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Training:</h2>
<p class="bac">
The training will include full instruction on all relevant tools, techniques and working practices. You&#39;ll also receive a solid grounding in all business areas, as you develop your professional skills and teamwork capabilities.  
</p>
<p class="bac">
Once you join a business line, you will take on real responsibility from an early stage. There will be exposure to on&ndash;going development opportunities throughout the programme and you&#39;ll be encouraged to expand your abilities through on&ndash;the&ndash;job learning, structured training and study towards professional qualifications. The company fosters an inclusive and supportive culture in which hard work is rewarded.  
</p>

